SECURITY DISCLAIMER

This software handles sensitive authentication credentials and API keys.
Users should:

1. Never commit API keys or credentials to version control
2. Use environment variables for all sensitive configuration
3. Regularly rotate API keys and access tokens
4. Only use on trusted development machines
5. Follow Esper security guidelines for API access

The authors are not responsible for any security breaches or misuse
of credentials when using this software.